mt7601u: use DEFINE_DEBUGFS_ATTRIBUTE to define debugfs fops

It is more clear to use DEFINE_DEBUGFS_ATTRIBUTE to define debugfs file
operation rather than DEFINE_SIMPLE_ATTRIBUTE.

